    FROM "Chats" AS c
    INNER JOIN "Agents" AS a ON c."AgentId" = a."Id"
    INNER JOIN "Customers" AS c0 ON c."CustomerId" = c0."Id"
    WHERE c."Id" = @__chatId_0 AND (a."Email" = @__email_1 OR c0."Email" = @__email_1))

    FROM "Chats" AS c

    WHERE c."Id" = @__chatId_0 AND (a."Email" = @__email_1 OR c0."Email" = @__email_1))

    FROM "Chats" AS c
    INNER JOIN "Agents" AS a ON c."AgentId" = a."Id"
    INNER JOIN "Customers" AS c0 ON c."CustomerId" = c0."Id"
    WHERE c."Id" = @__chatId_0 AND (a."Email" = @__email_1 OR c0."Email" = @__email_1))

    FROM "Chats" AS c
    INNER JOIN "Agents" AS a ON c."AgentId" = a."Id"

    WHERE c."Id" = @__chatId_0 AND (a."Email" = @__email_1 OR c0."Email" = @__email_1))

    FROM "Chats" AS c
    INNER JOIN "Agents" AS a ON c."AgentId" = a."Id"
    INNER JOIN "Customers" AS c0 ON c."CustomerId" = c0."Id"
    WHERE c."Id" = @__chatId_0 AND (a."Email" = @__email_1 OR c0."Email" = @__email_1))

    FROM "Chats" AS c
    INNER JOIN "Agents" AS a ON c."AgentId" = a."Id"
    INNER JOIN "Customers" AS c0 ON c."CustomerId" = c0."Id"
    WHERE c."Id" = @__chatId_0 AND (a."Email" = @__email_1 OR c0."Email" = @__email_1))
